audio_descriptions.notes:
Annie:
- A young woman named Cindy is seen approaching the front door of a house with her luggage pulled behind her
- She reaches toward the doorbell but hesitates and instead pulls out her pocket mirror to double check her appearance
- Looking satisfied with her appearance she rings the doorbell and a man named James, opens the door
- She gives a big smile and James excitedly opens his arms for a hug
- She steps towards him but something catches her attention towards the couch
- it is Phil, a green elephant sitting on the couch waving at her
- She waves back and says... 
- Looking back at James, she gives him a dirty look
- We now see Phil on the couch slurping away at a drink from a purple cup 
- The couple are now in the James' bedroom, having a heated conversation
- Cindy questions James...
- Phil gets startled at Cindy's screaming but continues to sip his drink
-  "The Elephant in the room" 
- As James walks infront of Phil to take a seat beside him, Phil spanks him
- James glares at Phil and tackles him causing the couch to fall backward
- Cindy walks upstairs and replaces the picture of James and Phil with pictures of herself with James 
- Cindy opens her luggage and grabs a towel and heads to the bathroom
- Turning off the sink and looking refreshed, Cindy tilts the mirror above the sink back and is shocked to find Phil in the reflection, sitting on the toilet holding a book 
- Cindy lets out a scream and Phil runs screaming out of the bathroom towards James who is in the kitchen
- Phil runs into the counter and falls on his back
- Breathing heavily, Phil reaches out towards James but James just walks away shaking his head in disbelief
- As Phil lays there on the kitchen floor, his stomach starts to rumble
- He sits up and sees this angelic light emitting onto the fridge 
- He intensely stares at the fridge and finally decides to slowly open the fridge door
- The room is now pitch black and the only light comes from the opened fridge
- Phil stands in front of the open fridge and is mesmerized by whats inside the fridge

Sarah:
- Cindy is sitting on the bed, angry. The door opens, James' head pokes in.
-He holds a stuffed bear, Mr. Pepper, and says..
- Cindy glares at James and rips the stuffed bear’s head off
- James runs from the room and into the kitchen, where his expression turns to shock. Cindy enters the room too. 
-Phil is eating hungrily from the fridge
-He stops eating, turns around and grows larger
-James stares and says... Cindy nods her head
-Utensils are pulled from the drawer, plates are put down on a table and a pizza slice is lifted from a pizza box
-Red wine is poured into a glass and the record player is turned on 
-James pulls his chair out and sits across from Cindy, staring at her and a smile appears on his face
-He reaches across the table and takes her hand in his 
-while holding hands, a vacuum noise causes their gazes to turn away from each other to Phil, standing beside them.
-James sighs and Cindy glares at him.
-A pizza slice flies in the air and is sucked into Phil's mouth, causing him to choke. 
- James is laughing, Cindy starts yelling at him
-James jumps up and performs the Heimlich maneuver
-The pizza slice shoots out of the Phil's mouth and hits Cindy in the face, knocking her out of her chair.
-James and Phil stare in silence, then burst out laughing, Phil falls back from laughter
-Cindy and James sit across from each other on their bed with their backs turned to each other.
-Cindy is angry and James looks to her, worried and he goes to reach for her but stops
-Frustrated, Cindy huffs and lies down on her side, reaching to the light on her nightstand and clicks it off 
-James is left in the dark and lies on his back where he sighs


Herleen:
4:03-4-39
-Phil lets out a sigh and bounces up from the couch.
-He starts to turn into a giant and breaks the furniture around him, taking up all of  the room in the house.
-In the morning, Cindy wakes up from her sleep. Her eyes widen as she looks up at the sky. She sits up and finds herself and James outside of their home. 
-She  packs her clothes into a suitcase. 
-Her back is turned towards James and Phil.
-James lets out a sigh and turns around to look up at Phil. 
-Phil’s trunk wraps around James face and Phil becomes his normal size. 
-Cindy holds on to James shoulder
-they both watch Phil in disbelief as he lugs the refrigerator out the door.
- Phil shuts the door on his way out.
-James picks up Phil’s purple cup that Phil doodled on. It has the word Starfucks written on it and a drawing of an elephant mermaid. He stares at it with a sad look on his face
-While holding the  headless stuffed animal from earlier, Cindy waves it in front of James’s 
The film cuts to a black screen with the word fin on it. It then moves on to the closing credits.
-Credits: 
-A film by Angith, Apoorva, Arunabh, Deep, denise, Keerthi and Preetish. 
-Voices of Ethan Reitz, Dan Griner, and Valerie Ralliere. Music by Filip Fejtl. Emma’s Song by Rick Braun. Sound by Luke Goldfinch. 
-Thanks to Faculty, Krushnakant K and Ashray S	

-Described by Annie, Sarah and Herleen

CGI 3D Animated Short Film: "The Elephant in the Room Short Film" by Angith Jayarajan, Apoorva Chitnis, Arunabh Deoraj, Deep Dawda, 
Denise Noronha, Keerthi Prasad, Preetish Jayarajan. Featured on http://www.cgmeetup.net/

"The Elephant in the Room" is a 3d animated graduation short film from RUBIKA SUPINFOCOM, DSKIC. The film is about James and his best friend Phil and what happens when James' girlfriend Cindy, decides to move in.
